Controls

 * left click: select unit
 * drag rect: select multiple  units
 * right click: deselect selected units

Tech

simple vehicle steering behaviour as desribed in http://www.red3d.com/cwr/steer/gdc99/

Todos

 * ammunition
 * behaviour: follow / arrival
 * glow
 * scrollable playing field
 * server


